07/07/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- US Defence Secretary Donald Rumsfeld sent a letter expressing full support for the Albanian Army's reforms, according to a report Sunday (6 July) by ATA.
Rumsfeld expressed thanks for the warm welcome he received while visiting Tirana last month.
He spoke highly of Albania's role in the region, saying "Albania has given an important contribution to regional and international security." (ATA, BBC - 06/07/03)
